com.mappedin.sdk

Interface LocationGenerator


  • public interface LocationGenerator
    This interface defines a custom LocationGenerator. A custom LocationGenerator is a way to generate locations with more than the default properties, if they are present in the Mappedin CMS.
    If you think you need this, ask Mappedin to help set it up.
